===Noun===
'''{{ARchar|شَجَرٌ}}''' (šádžar) ''m (collective)'', '''{{ARchar|شَجَرَةٌ}}''' (šádžara) ''f ([[singulative]])'', '''{{ARchar|شَجَرْتَيْنِ}}''' (šadžartéːn) ''(dual)'', '''{{ARchar|شَجَرَاتٌ}}''' (šadžaráːt) ''([[paucal]])'', '''{{ARchar|أشْجَارٌ}}''' (‘ašdžáːr) ''(pl.)''

# [[tree]]


*{{ARchar|شَجَرٌ}} (šádžar) = trees (in general) ''(plural in meaning, but grammatically singular)''
*{{ARchar|ٌشَجَرَة}} (šádžara) = a tree
*{{ARchar|شَجَرْتَيْنِ}} (šadžartéːn) = two trees
*{{ARchar|شَجَرَاتٌ}} (šadžaráːt) = 3 to 10 trees, some trees, a few trees ''(little plural)''
*{{ARchar|أشْجَارٌ}} (‘ašdžáːr) = (kinds of) trees ''(big plural)''

